data.description: Enjoy Abundant Space in this Attractive 3BR/2.5 Bath Home in Valleybrook Subdivision! Just 3 minutes to AL A&M University, this home would make an excellent investment property. Open floor plan including formal dining room & living, plus a large family/media room on the 2nd level. The kitchen features a work island & serving window to dining. New high efficiency HVAC installed in May 2023. Spacious master suite with HUGE walk-in closet, double basin vanity & jetted tub. Enjoy covered porches at the front & rear of home, privacy fenced backyard with 2- Storage buildings. Full brick exterior. Easy commute to downtown HSV, Madison & Hazel Green. 100% Financing Available w/PATH loan.
